#$Id#

adore service registry command line tool


INTRODUCITON

 This toolset allows modificaiton and inspect of adore service
 registry from command line, another goal is to avoid error-prone xml
 processing. 

These tools talk to service registry OAI-PMH or RegistryHandler web service.


CONFIGURATION

Configuration should be done in env.sh, it includes major environment variable setup.

USAGE

add.sh: add a new collection to service registry 
	add.sh <collection> <identifier> <created time> 

delete.sh: delete a collection or service
	 delete.sh <identifier>

list.sh: list all collections or services
	list.sh <collection|service>

get.sh: get a record 
	 get.sh <identifier>
	
